 ($\\varepsilon$-approximate)\nShapley Indices Partial Inverse Power Index Problem.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 19 Jul 2020 05:54:29 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 26 Jul 2020 21:03:39 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-07-28"}
