 challenge; while the planet-star contrast at\neclipse and planet flux are accessible with a 6-8m space telescope, the\nplanet-star separation is 1/3 - 1/4 of the angular separation limit of modern\ncoronagraphy.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 19 Jul 2020 08:48:34 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 21 Jul 2020 15:59:22 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-09-02"}
